page.title: 12WORTHEN GARAGE
page.content:
The garage at Worthen originally sold petrol,sweets,and cigarettes.In recent years it has expanded to repair cars,and to sell secondhand cars.It has also become a village "bazaar".A survey of what people have purchased from the "garage"shows:_
Petrol 21 Chips 9 Glue 3 Bread 16 Peas 12 Pumps 5 Crisps 18 Leads 1 Wood 3 Sugar 15 Coal 9 Magazines 12 Milk 15 Eggs 14 Icecream 16 Sauces 8 Cards 13 Yoghurt 10 Comics 15 Bulbs 13 Batteries 13 Fruit 14 Books 7 Vegetable 15 Drinks 17 Videos 7 Biscuits 17 Toys 9 Pens 13 Lighters 16 Papers 17 Meat 10 Butter 12 Pegs 8 Seeds 8 Cereals 9 Pies 10 Tins 12 Envelopes 8
